Name: Emperial Knights
About the game: You incarnate as a powerful knight of the Emperial Kingdom to bring justice and honor through your adventure in the world. Fast Paced Action Combat and Open World Adventure. Features: Classes : Create your own character with a progression. The classes are : Warrior, Ranger, Mage, Assassin, Pistolero. Parkour : You can wall climb/run or slide anything, anytime. Tower of Infinite : Spawning waves of monsters and bosses infinitely. PVP : Press Tab, Hover your mouse on your friend and Press P in order to duel them on a deadly duel. Party : Group up with your friends and start an adventure together. Local Multiplayer : Host and Join games via IP address.
